data.description: **Price Adjustment** Welcome to your dream home! This charming 4-bedroom , 3 full bathroom home in Hampton, Georgia.  Step inside to discover generously sized living room and dinning room, lovely family room with fireplace creating the perfect space for gathering and relaxation, open kitchen concept with island plus a large pantry for all your storage needs, great for preparing meals and entertaining guest. On the main floor you will also find 1 bedroom and a full bath for your guests. The second floor has 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths plus the laundry room. The large size master bedroom offers a generous WALK-IN CLOSET, a double vanity, and a separate tub and shower for added comfort. A two-car attached garage provides convenient parking and additional storage space. Step out to the large backyard, perfect place for a backyard bbq, garden and entertainment, and fully fenced in for the kids or pets to run around.
